metadata.name: Not Alone #1/10
metadata.description:
This is a piece of gratitude to God almighty and to all the amazing people who supported my journey as an artist, thereby, giving me hope and making this journey worth it.  

Its a piece to remind everyone that; irrespective of what you are going through in life, your career, relationship etc. sooner or later, someone will divinely show up in your life that will lead and see you through. 

"But the Helper, the Holy Spirit, whom the Father will send in My name, He will teach you all things, and bring to your remembrance all things that I said to you."

John 14 vs 26
